''Embarrassment of Riches'' is an 6-song "albumette" by [[Elephant Micah]] which was released [[September 29]], [[2006]] on Micah's own [[LRRC (Luddite Rural Recording Cooperative)|LRRC]] label. The record was be unveiled at a record release party at Micah's alma mater, [[Earlham College]]. 

